   - Proper error handling for missing API key and API failures
   - Matches existing VocabularyEntry model

3. **`src/features/vocabulary/components/ReviewMode.tsx`** — Review component with:
   - Four review modes: Word → Meaning, Meaning → Word, Gap-fill, Collocation
   - SM-2 spaced repetition using existing `src/lib/spaced-repetition.ts` library
   - Rating buttons (Again / Hard / Good / Easy)
   - Progress bar and stats
   - Completion summary screen
   - Theme CSS variables (no hardcoded colors)
